snippet.title: AZAZEL Gameplay
snippet.description:
https://subalterngames.itch.io/azazel

AZAZEL is a short roguelike about goats, sin, and the Bible.

In the Book of Leviticus, one goat is sacrificed, and one is sent into the wilderness.

But the sacrificed goat survived. Where it goes, sin and chaos follow.

You are that goat. Find the other goat.
